snippet.title: Eggy - Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST HERE: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1523670/Eggy/

Eggy is a 2.5D physics platformer with golf like controls, set in a beautiful environment. Egg-splore the world by jumping, rolling, swimming and bouncing in search for Eggy's mom. Where could she be?
